_aLatestUpdates._sText: That's the last update, nothing needs to be edited now.

_aChangeLog.text: Placed an entity controlling the weapons at spawn, instead of weapons under the spawnpoints

_sText:
AWP High Bullet Flow

Two Skyscrapers in a big city, connected with a plank (sounds strange, isn't it? :D)

It took me about 5 days to make this map.

FEATURES:

  • HDR
  • Cubemaps
  • Dust motes
  • Dynamic smoke around the skyscrapers
  • Seagulls (they exist, but CS:S does not support birds)
  • NODRAW, func_detail and lightmap optimisation
Version 2:

  • new sky (tides)
  • fixed spawnpoints and AWP when spawning
  • some bug fixes
Version 3:

  • Fixed the weapons at last
  • added some sun rays (volumetric light (my custom texture))
Version 4 (last one)

  • Fixed cubemaps

Enjoy the map :)
